@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.28 - v2 + 0.05)) * 0.30)
    v0 = wp.sin(0.76)
    v2 = (0.93 / 0.06)
    v0 = (0.26 + ((v2 + 0.21 / v0 + 0.82) / wp.sin(v0 + 0.91)))
    v1 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.53 / tmp + 0.77)) / (v0 + 0.21))
    tmp = 0.49
    tmp = v1
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
